powerpc: Replace _ALIGN_DOWN() by ALIGN_DOWN()

_ALIGN_DOWN() is specific to powerpc
ALIGN_DOWN() is generic and does the same

Replace _ALIGN_DOWN() by ALIGN_DOWN()

